item.description: I thought I'd switch it up a little...How about meeting for Breakfast at Leo's before the walk?....We'll end up finishing earlier too and have more of the day left afterwards...I was going to move the walks to earlier in the day for the summer anyway, so let's try this! It'll be fun, you can watch me polish off the He-Man Special...Any objections?
item.how_to_find_us: Tiara and Hoodie...you can't miss me...
